" Source: Google XML Document Format Style Guide,
" https://google.github.io/styleguide/xmlstyle.html
" Date: 21/06/2020

" Do not use the tab key, i.e. use spaces instead of tabs.
set expandtab

" Documents MAY be pretty-printed using 2-space indentation for child elements.
set softtabstop=2
set shiftwidth=2
